Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_mem_debug2

Notes: Internal per-port state intended for debug use only - pko_prt_psb.head[63:0] This CSR is a memory of 12 entries, and thus, the PKO_REG_READ_IDX CSR must be written before any CSR read operations to this address can be performed.
